org.apache.ctakes.dictionary.lookup2.textspan

Class DefaultTextSpan

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ctakes.dictionary.lookup2.textspan.DefaultTextSpan
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TextSpan

    public final class DefaultTextSpan
extends java.lang.Object
implements TextSpan
    A useful key for hash collections based upon start and end indices. This is faster than using String as String.hashCode() iterates over the internal character array of a new string (new(..), .substring(..), .lowercase(..), ...).
